The paper deals with the development of an algorithm for automated brain extraction from MRI images using artificial neural networks. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG), as the algorithm relies on deep learning techniques. Additionally, the use of neural networks suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and multimedia (cs.MM).
